I"<h1 id="self-improvement-hook">Self-Improvement Hook</h1>

<p>Injects a reminder to evaluate learnings during agent bootstrap.</p>

<h2 id="what-it-does">What It Does</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Fires on <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">agent:bootstrap</code> (before workspace files are injected)</li>
  <li>Adds a reminder block to check <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.learnings/</code> for relevant entries</li>
  <li>Prompts the agent to log corrections, errors, and discoveries</li>
</ul>

<h2 id="configuration">Configuration</h2>

<p>No configuration needed. Enable with:</p>

<div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>openclaw hooks <span class="nb">enable </span>self-improvement
</code></pre></div></div>
